a series of functions which used for summarizing, finding max/min number, finding the average
and also counting:

Function:                Description:
--------                 -----------

SUM                      summarizing a group of numbers.

AVG                      finding the average in a group of numbers.

MAX                      finding the maximum number.

MIN                      finding the minimum number.

COUNT                    counting the amount of rows.



finding MAX:

=> SELECT MAX(price) AS mxprice FROM products;

finding MIN with ROUND:

=> SELECT ROUND( MIN(price), 2 ) AS miprice FROM products;

finding AVG:

=> SELECT ROUND( AVG(price), 2 ) AS avg FROM products;

